snippet: The municipal prosecutor’s office announced without comment on Thursday that it would not press charges in a fist-flinging altercation involving former Gov. Sarah Palin and her family at a party.
abstract: Alaska's municipal prosecutor's office says that it will not press charges in brawl involving former Gov Sarah Palin and her family that broke out at a party in Anchorage.
lead_paragraph: The municipal prosecutor’s office announced without comment on Thursday that it would not press charges in a fist-flinging altercation involving former Gov. Sarah Palin and her family at a party.

headline.main: No Charges Are Pressed Over Brawl With Palins
headline.print_headline: No Charges Are Pressed Over Brawl With Palins
